OL,3,CThousands of takeaway riders to strike
OL,4,Con Valentine's Day
OL,6,FThousands of delivery drivers for food-
OL,7,Fordering platforms, including
OL,8,FDeliveroo, Just Eat, and Uber Eats,
OL,9,Fare staging a Valentine's Day strike,
OL,10,Fdemanding better pay and conditions.
OL,12,FDelivery Job UK has organised the
OL,13,FValentine's Day industrial action,
OL,14,Fclaiming to have more than 3,000
OL,15,Fmembers prepared to down tools in
OL,16,FLondon alone.
OL,18,FThe grassroots organisation hopes to
OL,19,Ffocus attention on low pay and
OL,20,Finsecure conditions faced by drivers.
