OL,4,Con Valentine's Day
OL,6,FDue to app-based delivery drivers
OL,7,Fbeing designated as self-employed
OL,8,Fcontractors, they are not legally
OL,9,Fentitled to the national living wage
OL,10,Fof #10.42 and hour - which is due to
OL,11,Fincrease to #11.44 in April.
OL,13,FWriting on X, Delivery Job UK said:
OL,14,F"This Valentine's Day strike
OL,15,Fhighlights the growing tensions
OL,16,Fbetween gig economy workers and the
OL,17,Fplatforms they work for.
OL,19,F"As consumers, it's crucial to
OL,20,Fconsider the conditions under which
OL,21,Four conveniences are delivered.
