OL,3,CThousands of takeaway riders to strike
OL,4,Con Valentine's Day
OL,6,F"Let's stand in solidarity with those
OL,7,Ffighting for fair wages and better
OL,8,Fworking conditions. It's more than
OL,9,Fjust a meal at stake - it's about the
OL,10,Fdignity and rights of every worker."
OL,12,FThe mooted strike action comes after a
OL,13,Fcourt ruling that riders cannot be
OL,14,Fclassed as "workers" and do not have
OL,15,Fthe ability to form a union.
