OL,4,Con Valentine's Day
OL,6,FIn November, the Independent Worker's
OL,7,FUnion of Great Britain said: "The
OL,8,FSupreme Court's ruling comes as a
OL,9,Fdisappointment after years spent
OL,10,Ffighting a legal battle to secure
OL,11,Friders' bare minimum employment rights.
OL,13,F"As a union we cannot accept that
OL,14,Fthousands of riders should be working
OL,15,Fwithout key protections like the right
OL,16,Fto collective bargaining, and we will
OL,17,Fcontinue to make that case using all
OL,18,Favenues available to us, including
OL,19,Fconsidering our options under
OL,20,Finternational law."
