OL,6,FThe strike action also comes as
OL,7,FDeliveroo launched a partnership with
OL,8,FAnn Summers at the beginning of
OL,9,FFebruary in the run up to Valentine's
OL,10,FDay - with consumers able to get
OL,11,Fproducts from the lingerie and sex
OL,12,Ftoys vendor delivered to their home.
OL,14,FA Deliveroo spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Deliveroo aims to provide riders with
OL,16,Fthe flexible work riders tell us they
OL,17,Fvalue, attractive earning
OL,18,Fopportunities and protections.
