OL,6,F"Rider retention rates are high and
OL,7,Fthe overwhelming majority of riders
OL,8,Ftell us that they are satisfied
OL,9,Fworking with us.
OL,11,F"We value dialogue with riders, which
OL,12,Fis why we have a voluntary partnership
OL,13,Fagreement with a trade union, which
OL,14,Fincludes annual discussions on pay.
OL,16,F"We are pleased to also be able to
OL,17,Foffer riders free insurance, sickness
OL,18,Fcover, financial support when riders
OL,19,Fbecome new parents and a range of
OL,20,Ftraining opportunities."
