OL,6,FA Just Eat spokesperson added: "We
OL,7,Ftake the concerns of all couriers on
OL,8,Fthe Just Eat network extremely
OL,9,Fseriously. Their welfare is important
OL,10,Fto us, and we welcome their feedback.
OL,11,F"Our data shows that couriers
OL,12,Fdelivering for Just Eat earn, on
OL,13,Faverage, significantly over both the
OL,14,FLondon and national living wage for
OL,15,Fthe time they are on an order.J"We
OL,16,Fprovide a highly competitive base rate
OL,17,Fto self-employed couriers and have a
OL,18,Fgood relationship with the vast
OL,19,Fmajority of couriers across our
OL,20,Fnetwork. In addition, we offer regular
OL,21,Fincentives to help them maximise their
OL,22,Fearnings and continue to review our
OL,23,Fpay structure regularly."
